      <section id="section_nlp_zbf_rhb">
         <title>Working with the storage system</title>
         <ul>
            <li>
               <p>Commercial CMSs – Remote editing, locking. </p>
            </li>
            <li>
               <p>Open Source version control systems – Local working copies, no editing
                  restrictions → conflicts. </p>
               <p><b>Hint</b>: Maybe you can use the same storage system as software developers in
                  your company. </p>
            </li>
         </ul>
      </section>
      <section id="section_c4b_ccf_rhb">
         <title>Collaboration and Workflow</title>
